Package: dimControl
Title: Dimensional Control Tools for Steel Panels
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
      person("Nataly", "Romaris", , "nataly.romaris@udc.es", role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Olamar", "Benavente", role = "aut"),
      person("Ruben", "Fernandez-Casal", role = "aut"),
      person("Salvador", "Naya", role = "aut"),
      person("Javier", "Tarrio-Saavedra", role = "aut")
      )
Maintainer: Nataly Romaris <nataly.romaris@udc.es>
Description: R package developed by the MODES group for the dimensional control of 
    steel panels in naval construction. It provides tools for geometric processing, bounding 
    box computation, panel border extraction, directional angle estimation, detection 
    of disconnected components, and other functions to support analysis and scientific publications.
